### Variables de entorno
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/reserva
@auth = Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

### Obtener todas las reservas
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{auth}}

### Obtener una reserva por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/5
Authorization: {{auth}}

### Crear una nueva reserva
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{auth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juan Carlos",
  "apellido": "Pérez",
